data.description: Enjoy peaceful country living on 2.5 acres in this 3 bedroom 2 bath 1615 sq ft home on private water well. Built in 2021, this one-story stucco home embraces open concept living-granite kitchen with large island w/breakfast bar & ceramic wood-look tile throughout the entire home. Retreat to your primary bedroom with en-suite bath featuring large tile walk in shower w/Rain Shower & double granite vanities. Secondary bedroom can flex - it has a built in queen size Murphy bed! Plenty of room for your favorite hobbies & livestock show projects - there's already a chicken coop/equipment shed combo! Schedule your private showing today!
